This directory contains several simulation related tools:

i)   corsikaIOreader: transform CORSIKA telescope files (eventio format) into grisu format 
                      and/or fill root histograms with particle/Cherenkov photons properties
		      (see README.corsikaIOreader)

ii)  rosha:          read CORSIKA file and fill particles into root histograms
                     (see README.rosha)

iii) getThickness:   calculate atmospheric thickness [g/cm2] from given height [m]

iv)  getHeight:      calculate height [m] from atmospheric thickness [g/cm2]

v)   atmosphereAndCherenkovLight:   plot atmosphere and cherenkov properties from CORSIKA/KASCADE atmospheres

vi)  atmosphereCherenkovAbsorption: plot atmospheric absorption of Cherenkov photons

vii) getRunHeaderFromTelescopeFile: print run header from a CORSIKA telescope file

All data files (atmosphere and extinction values are in ./data)

